{"tid":1992612,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊岳橋: 在「內會」不會退縮","createTime":"2020-04-28T08:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T05:22:43.000Z","uid":134071,"like":341,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"3ee0a564457273c32fe9b86d7efbfe7d3d3f1db4","tid":1992612,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:58:44.000Z","msg":"公民黨主席親自講<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AlvinYeungCP/photos/a.637817586311649/2935421716551213/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAlvinYeungCP%2Fphotos%2Fa.637817586311649%2F2935421716551213%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=bfd22675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AlvinYeungCP/photos/a.637817586311649/2935421716551213/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\nAlvin Yeung 楊岳橋<br />\n8分鐘 &middot; <br />\n【回應消息人士】民主派內會「鬆手」？<br />\n<br />\n對於有報道引述消息人士透露、民主派將於內會鬆手放水，我已在剛才的記者會回應如下：<br />\n<br />\n「公民黨黨魁楊岳橋回應近日內會的爭議，指內會抗爭將近六個月，中聯辦及港澳辦聲明明顯是劍指郭榮鏗，郭亦清楚表達了他的立場，即使他被DQ 亦會是他一生的光榮。在這個前提下，公民黨是不會有退縮或退讓的空間，即使現在真的退下來，共產黨亦不會放過公民黨。<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋又指他雖然不能代表民主派，但表明公民黨於內會中非常積極發言、五名議員於內會發言超過90次，累積總時間6.5小時，並無半點鬆懈，立場亦不會因為任何情況而有所改變。他呼籲社會與其捕風捉影，不如繼續團結，繼續撐住內會。<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋續謂隨著選舉愈來愈近，或會有消息人士每日試圖帶領風向，製造不安。唯他表明公民黨不會退縮，會繼續按《議事規則》議事、積極發言。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/3dooHAN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3dooHAN.png&h=5e9f482c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fe307dcbe1b2fd5d74db12a4a30942aabe3409c","tid":1992612,"uid":54186,"like":40,"dislike":6,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:59:17.000Z","msg":"係先好講阿"},{"pid":"73927eb0cd2e731905f0f0a02681a6d2ed91804f","tid":1992612,"uid":134071,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:59:30.000Z","msg":"較早時聲明<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civicpartyhk/photos/a.450720993456/10157086218218457/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivicpartyhk%2Fphotos%2Fa.450720993456%2F10157086218218457%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=9c31f569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civicpartyhk/photos/a.450720993456/10157086218218457/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/om3soh6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fom3soh6.jpg&h=c892f79f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66a4ea8c0e6504e705009aad4461f358ecce094f","tid":1992612,"uid":134071,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"0fe307dcbe1b2fd5d74db12a4a30942aabe3409c","tid":1992612,"uid":54186,"like":40,"dislike":6,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:59:17.000Z","msg":"係先好講阿"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:59:47.000Z","msg":"泛民一縮, 肯定無左超個一半選票."},{"pid":"35047b9e5b58ce9ab772e8643049e6039d7e61bd","tid":1992612,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c240c05c9ee4b337aed1f37e1af744cb05de243","tid":1992612,"uid":310700,"like":89,"dislike":3,"score":86,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:00:16.000Z","msg":"你敢退就真係變dead body<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/28/170005_9dde8a5231d4eab3c990b6dd81889cdd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F28%2F170005_9dde8a5231d4eab3c990b6dd81889cdd.gif&h=664b7d01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0eb77effe2525cebbe4c61062866de32721fd1c2","tid":1992612,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:00:26.000Z","msg":"[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8c8917388e2df62382ab11f00dc